Just as useless as the last upload. Not zipped and broken.

But the quest is still. WTF is it and why are there exe windows files included?

FastForwarder...Do you really need to call the guy a retard? If you just go to the site with the actual software you will see its packaged that way with Mac/Win files together. Blame the developer.
